@startuml
title ElectroCorp Platform - Notifications Backend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Notifications Backend Bounded Context" {
  class "Application" as Backend_notifications_Application <<layer>>
  class "Domain" as Backend_notifications_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Backend_notifications_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Interfaces REST" as Backend_notifications_Interfaces_REST <<layer>>
}

Backend_notifications_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_notifications_Application : commands / queries
Backend_notifications_Application ..> Backend_notifications_Domain : model and policies
Backend_notifications_Application ..> Backend_notifications_Infrastructure : repository ports / adapters
Backend_notifications_Infrastructure ..> Backend_notifications_Domain : persistence mapping
Backend_notifications_Interfaces_REST ..> Backend_notifications_Domain : resources from aggregates

note bottom of Backend_notifications_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/backend/layers/notifications.
end note

@enduml
